Player Adjusts Settings

BASIC COURSE: 

The Player clicks the Settings button and the game brings them to the settings screen. The player then modifies the settings bar such as windowed/fullscreen mode, sound, music, brightness, and resolution. The player clicks the Save button and the game brings the player back to the title screen.
 
ALTERNATIVE COURSE:

Player clicks the exit button: The game completely exits without saving any of the settings.  

Player clicks the cancel button: The game will go back to the original settings without saving.
